name: Cane & Upholstered Bar Stool - Natural
description: The Cane & Upholstered Bar Stool - Natural features a handwoven natural cane backrest and a plush upholstered seat. The stool pairs the iconic silhouette with the comfort of an upholstered seat. The timeless geometric frame is made from solid teak. Handmade in Indonesia by skilled craftsmen.
